*Stojala je usamljena na peroni.(She was standing alone on the platform.)

*Čovek je stajao u hodniku.(The man was standing in the hallway.)

*Ona se osvrće preko ramena i *stoji* u nedoumici.(She looks over her shoulder and stands in confusion.)

*Rezultati su bili iznenađujući; niko nije *stojao* iza njih.(The results were surprising; no one stood behind them.)

*On je često *stojao* na istom mestu sutradan.(He often stood in the same place the next day.)